reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars solid grommets for my RV range
reviews.reviewText: This is a simple review as my RV is in storage for the winter.My existing rubber grommets have worn out. My RV is 18 years old.These feel very solid yet flexible enough for the grate legs to slip in.I look forward to installing these first thing in the spring as part of my Spring RV startup procedure.This look, feel, and flex as if they will last a long time. Very happy with the order.
